{"number":24,"verseCount":51,"verses":[[1,["And Jesus went out, and departed from the temple: and his disciples came to ",["him",["clarity-word"]]," for to ",["shew",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—M 1:2","pgp/js-m/1.2"],"."]]]," him the buildings of the ",["temple",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 45:20 (15–21)","dc-testament/dc/45.20"],". ",["TG Temple","tg/temple"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["And Jesus said unto them, ",["See",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 45:18","dc-testament/dc/45.18"],"."]]]," ye not all these things? verily I say unto you, There shall not be left here one ",["stone",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 19:44 (41–44)","nt/luke/19.44"],"; ",["JS—M 1:3 (1–55)","pgp/js-m/1.3"],"."]]]," upon another, that shall not be thrown down."]],[3,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"And as he sat upon the mount of Olives, the disciples came unto him privately, saying, Tell us, when shall these things be? and what ",["shall be",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["sign",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 21:7 (7–36)","nt/luke/21.7"],"; ",["D&C 45:16 (16–75)","dc-testament/dc/45.16"],"."]]]," of thy coming, and of the end of the ",["world",["study-note-ref","b",[["JS—M 1:4","pgp/js-m/1.4"]," adds “or the destruction of the wicked, which is the end of the world.” ",["D&C 45:22","dc-testament/dc/45.22"],". ",["TG Last Days","tg/last-days"],"; ",["World, End of","tg/world-end-of"],"."]]],"?"]],[4,["And Jesus answered and said unto them, Take heed that no man ",["deceive",["study-note-ref","a",[["Col. 2:18 (16–23)","nt/col/2.18"],"; ",["D&C 49:23 (22–24)","dc-testament/dc/49.23"],". ",["TG Lying","tg/lying"],"."]]]," you."]],[5,["For many shall come in my ",["name",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Name","tg/name"],"."]]],", saying, I am ",["Christ",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG False Christs","tg/false-christs"],"."]]],"; and shall ",["deceive",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mark 13:6","nt/mark/13.6"],". ",["TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church","tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"],"."]]]," many."]],[6,["And ye shal